#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.plot.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.plot"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:1 of
msgid "Make plots of Series or DataFrame."
msgstr "绘制 Series 或 DataFrame 的图表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:3 of
msgid ""
"Uses the backend specified by the option ``plotting.backend``. By "
"default, matplotlib is used."
msgstr "使用由选项 ``plotting.backend`` 指定的后端。默认情况下，使用 matplotlib。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:6 of
msgid "The object for which the method is called."
msgstr "调用该方法的对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:8 of
msgid "Only used if data is a DataFrame."
msgstr "仅在 data 是 DataFrame 时使用。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:10 of
msgid ""
"Allows plotting of one column versus another. Only used if data is a "
"DataFrame."
msgstr "允许绘制一列与另一列的对比图。仅在 data 是 DataFrame 时使用。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:13 of
msgid ""
"The kind of plot to produce:  - 'line' : line plot (default) - 'bar' : "
"vertical bar plot - 'barh' : horizontal bar plot - 'hist' : histogram - "
"'box' : boxplot - 'kde' : Kernel Density Estimation plot - 'density' : "
"same as 'kde' - 'area' : area plot - 'pie' : pie plot - 'scatter' : "
"scatter plot (DataFrame only) - 'hexbin' : hexbin plot (DataFrame only)"
msgstr ""
"要生成的图表类型：  - 'line' : 折线图（默认） - 'bar' : 垂直条形图 - '"
"barh' : 水平条形图 - 'hist' : 直方图 - 'box' : 箱线图 - 'kde' : 核"
"密度估计图 - 'density' : 与 'kde' 相同 - 'area' : 面积图 - 'pie' : 饼图 -"
" 'scatter' : 散点图（仅限 DataFrame） - 'hexbin' : 六边形箱图（仅限 "
"DataFrame）"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:13 of
msgid "The kind of plot to produce:"
msgstr "要生成的绘图类型："

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:15 of
msgid "'line' : line plot (default)"
msgstr "'line' : 折线图（默认）"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:16 of
msgid "'bar' : vertical bar plot"
msgstr "'bar' : 垂直条形图"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:17 of
msgid "'barh' : horizontal bar plot"
msgstr "'barh' : 水平条形图"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:18 of
msgid "'hist' : histogram"
msgstr "'hist' : 直方图"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:19 of
msgid "'box' : boxplot"
msgstr "'box' : 箱线图"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:20 of
msgid "'kde' : Kernel Density Estimation plot"
msgstr "'kde' : 核密度估计图"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:21 of
msgid "'density' : same as 'kde'"
msgstr "'density' : 与 'kde' 相同"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:22 of
msgid "'area' : area plot"
msgstr "'area' : 面积图"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:23 of
msgid "'pie' : pie plot"
msgstr "'pie' : 饼图"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:24 of
msgid "'scatter' : scatter plot (DataFrame only)"
msgstr "'scatter' : 散点图（仅 DataFrame）"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:25 of
msgid "'hexbin' : hexbin plot (DataFrame only)"
msgstr "'hexbin' : 六边形箱图（仅 DataFrame）"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:27 of
msgid "An axes of the current figure."
msgstr "当前图形的一个坐标轴。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:29 of
msgid ""
"Whether to group columns into subplots:  - ``False`` : No subplots will "
"be used - ``True`` : Make separate subplots for each column. - sequence "
"of iterables of column labels: Create a subplot for each   group of "
"columns. For example `[('a', 'c'), ('b', 'd')]` will   create 2 subplots:"
" one with columns 'a' and 'c', and one   with columns 'b' and 'd'. "
"Remaining columns that aren't specified   will be plotted in additional "
"subplots (one per column).    .. versionadded:: 1.5.0"
msgstr ""
"是否将列分组到子图中：  - ``False`` : 不使用子图 - ``True`` : 为每列创建"
"单独的子图。 - 列标签的可迭代序列：为每组列创建一个子图。例如 `[('a', 'c'"
"), ('b', 'd')]` 将创建 2 个子图：一个包含 'a' 和 'c' 列，另一个包含 'b' "
"和 'd' 列。未指定的其余列将在附加子图中绘制（每列一个子图）。    .. "
"versionadded:: 1.5.0"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:29 of
msgid "Whether to group columns into subplots:"
msgstr "是否将列分组到子图中："

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:31 of
msgid "``False`` : No subplots will be used"
msgstr "``False`` : 不会使用子图"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:32 of
msgid "``True`` : Make separate subplots for each column."
msgstr "``True`` : 为每列创建单独的子图。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:33 of
msgid ""
"sequence of iterables of column labels: Create a subplot for each group "
"of columns. For example `[('a', 'c'), ('b', 'd')]` will create 2 "
"subplots: one with columns 'a' and 'c', and one with columns 'b' and 'd'."
" Remaining columns that aren't specified will be plotted in additional "
"subplots (one per column)."
msgstr ""
"是否将列分组到子图中：  - ``False`` : 不使用子图 - ``True`` : 为每列创建"
"单独的子图。 - 列标签的可迭代序列：为每组列创建一个子图。例如 `[('a', 'c'"
"), ('b', 'd')]` 将创建 2 个子图：一个包含 'a' 和 'c' 列，另一个包含 'b' "
"和 'd' 列。未指定的其余列将在附加子图中绘制（每列一个子图）。    .. "
"versionadded:: 1.5.0"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:41 of
msgid ""
"In case ``subplots=True``, share x axis and set some x axis labels to "
"invisible; defaults to True if ax is None otherwise False if an ax is "
"passed in; Be aware, that passing in both an ax and ``sharex=True`` will "
"alter all x axis labels for all axis in a figure."
msgstr ""
"在 ``subplots=True`` 的情况下，共享 x 轴并将某些 x 轴标签设为不可见；如果"
" ax 为 None 则默认为 True，否则如果传入 ax 则默认为 False；请注意，同时"
"传入 ax 和 ``sharex=True`` 将会修改图中所有轴的 x 轴标签。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:46 of
msgid ""
"In case ``subplots=True``, share y axis and set some y axis labels to "
"invisible."
msgstr "在 ``subplots=True`` 的情况下，共享 y 轴并将某些 y 轴标签设为不可见。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:48 of
msgid "(rows, columns) for the layout of subplots."
msgstr "子图布局的（行数，列数）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:50 of
msgid "Size of a figure object."
msgstr "图形对象的大小。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:52 of
msgid "Use index as ticks for x axis."
msgstr "使用索引作为 x 轴的刻度。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:54 of
msgid ""
"Title to use for the plot. If a string is passed, print the string at the"
" top of the figure. If a list is passed and `subplots` is True, print "
"each item in the list above the corresponding subplot."
msgstr ""
"用于绘图的标题。如果传入字符串，则将其打印在图形顶部；如果传入列表且 `"
"subplots` 为 True，则将列表中每个元素打印在对应子图上方。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:58 of
msgid "Axis grid lines."
msgstr "坐标轴网格线。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:60 of
msgid "Place legend on axis subplots."
msgstr "在坐标轴子图上放置图例。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:62 of
msgid "The matplotlib line style per column."
msgstr "每列的 matplotlib 线条样式。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:64 of
msgid "Use log scaling or symlog scaling on x axis."
msgstr "在 x 轴上使用对数或对称对数缩放。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:66 of
msgid "Use log scaling or symlog scaling on y axis."
msgstr "在 y 轴上使用对数或对称对数缩放。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:68 of
msgid "Use log scaling or symlog scaling on both x and y axes."
msgstr "在 x 和 y 轴上都使用对数或对称对数缩放。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:70 of
msgid "Values to use for the xticks."
msgstr "用于 x 轴刻度的值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:72 of
msgid "Values to use for the yticks."
msgstr "用于 y 轴刻度的值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:74 of
msgid "Set the x limits of the current axes."
msgstr "设置当前坐标轴的 x 轴范围。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:76 of
msgid "Set the y limits of the current axes."
msgstr "设置当前坐标轴的 y 轴范围。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:78 of
msgid ""
"Name to use for the xlabel on x-axis. Default uses index name as xlabel, "
"or the x-column name for planar plots.  .. versionchanged:: 2.0.0      "
"Now applicable to histograms."
msgstr ""
"用于 x 轴标签的名称。默认使用索引名作为 xlabel，或者对于平面图使用 x 列名"
"。.. versionchanged:: 2.0.0 现适用于直方图。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:78 of
msgid ""
"Name to use for the xlabel on x-axis. Default uses index name as xlabel, "
"or the x-column name for planar plots."
msgstr ""
"用于 x 轴标签的名称。默认使用索引名作为 xlabel，或者对于平面图使用 x 列名"
"。.. versionchanged:: 2.0.0 现适用于直方图。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:83
#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:90 of
msgid "Now applicable to histograms."
msgstr "现在适用于直方图。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:85 of
msgid ""
"Name to use for the ylabel on y-axis. Default will show no ylabel, or the"
" y-column name for planar plots.  .. versionchanged:: 2.0.0      Now "
"applicable to histograms."
msgstr ""
"用于 y 轴标签的名称。默认不显示 ylabel，或者对于平面图使用 y 列名。.. "
"versionchanged:: 2.0.0 现适用于直方图。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:85 of
msgid ""
"Name to use for the ylabel on y-axis. Default will show no ylabel, or the"
" y-column name for planar plots."
msgstr ""
"用于 y 轴标签的名称。默认不显示 ylabel，或者对于平面图使用 y 列名。.. "
"versionchanged:: 2.0.0 现适用于直方图。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:92 of
msgid "Rotation for ticks (xticks for vertical, yticks for horizontal plots)."
msgstr "刻度旋转（垂直图为 xticks，水平图为 yticks）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:95 of
msgid "Font size for xticks and yticks."
msgstr "xticks 和 yticks 的字体大小。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:97 of
msgid ""
"Colormap to select colors from. If string, load colormap with that name "
"from matplotlib."
msgstr "选择颜色的色彩映射。如果是字符串，则从 matplotlib 中加载该名称的色彩映射。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:100 of
msgid "If True, plot colorbar (only relevant for 'scatter' and 'hexbin' plots)."
msgstr "如果为 True，则绘制颜色条（仅适用于 'scatter' 和 'hexbin' 图）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:103 of
msgid ""
"Specify relative alignments for bar plot layout. From 0 (left/bottom-end)"
" to 1 (right/top-end). Default is 0.5 (center)."
msgstr ""
"指定条形图布局的相对对齐方式。从 0（左/下端）到 1（右/上端）。默认为 0.5"
"（居中）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:107 of
msgid ""
"If True, draw a table using the data in the DataFrame and the data will "
"be transposed to meet matplotlib's default layout. If a Series or "
"DataFrame is passed, use passed data to draw a table."
msgstr ""
"如果为 True，则使用 DataFrame 中的数据绘制表格，并将数据转置以符合 "
"matplotlib 的默认布局。如果传入 Series 或 DataFrame，则使用传入的数据绘制"
"表格。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:112 of
msgid "See :ref:`Plotting with Error Bars <visualization.errorbars>` for detail."
msgstr "详见 :ref:`带误差条的绘图 <visualization.errorbars>`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:115 of
msgid "Equivalent to yerr."
msgstr "等同于 yerr。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:117 of
msgid "If True, create stacked plot."
msgstr "如果为 True，则创建堆叠图。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:119 of
msgid ""
"Whether to plot on the secondary y-axis if a list/tuple, which columns to"
" plot on secondary y-axis."
msgstr "是否绘制到次级 y 轴；如果为列表/元组，则指定哪些列绘制到次级 y 轴上。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:122 of
msgid ""
"When using a secondary_y axis, automatically mark the column labels with "
"\"(right)\" in the legend."
msgstr "使用 secondary_y 轴时，在图例中标记列标签为 \"(right)\"。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:125 of
msgid "If True, boolean values can be plotted."
msgstr "如果为 True，则可以绘制布尔值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:127 of
msgid ""
"Backend to use instead of the backend specified in the option "
"``plotting.backend``. For instance, 'matplotlib'. Alternatively, to "
"specify the ``plotting.backend`` for the whole session, set "
"``pd.options.plotting.backend``."
msgstr ""
"要使用的后端，而不是在选项 ``plotting.backend`` 中指定的后端。例如，'"
"matplotlib'。或者，要为整个会话指定 ``plotting.backend``，请设置 ``pd."
"options.plotting.backend``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:132 of
msgid "Options to pass to matplotlib plotting method."
msgstr "要传递给 matplotlib 绘图方法的选项。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:134 of
msgid ""
"If the backend is not the default matplotlib one, the return value will "
"be the object returned by the backend."
msgstr "如果后端不是默认的 matplotlib 后端，则返回值将是后端返回的对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:136 of
msgid ":class:`matplotlib.axes.Axes` or numpy.ndarray of them"
msgstr ":class:`matplotlib.axes.Axes` 或其 numpy.ndarray"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:139 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:140 of
msgid "See matplotlib documentation online for more on this subject"
msgstr "有关此主题的更多信息，请参阅在线 matplotlib 文档"

#: maxframe.dataframe.accessors.plotting.core.SeriesPlotAccessor:141 of
msgid ""
"If `kind` = 'bar' or 'barh', you can specify relative alignments for bar "
"plot layout by `position` keyword. From 0 (left/bottom-end) to 1 (right"
"/top-end). Default is 0.5 (center)"
msgstr ""
"如果 `kind` = 'bar' 或 'barh'，您可以通过 `position` 关键字指定条形图布局"
"的相对对齐方式。从 0（左/底端）到 1（右/顶端）。默认值为 0.5（居中）"

